{
  "stem": "4830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were supervising us, and they discovered that we left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in Csepel, this was a very strict military environment, and they were also probably afraid.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What if they discovered this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We did not want to escape permanently, because they said that if we escaped they will hold our family responsible, and secondly, we had no place to go.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we returned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We knew that they discovered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after our return, it was a very unpleasant Sunday afternoon, because there were six of us who returned voluntarily, including Tom [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Lantos, ?] who was with me in this military unit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they decided to teach us a lesson, and they were beating us for about one and a half hours in one shift.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when they got tired, they stopped, and then they started it again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With their fists, with sticks, with their belts-- whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I distinctly remember that I discovered that Corporal [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Brannard ?] is so tight that he cannot really hit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told my friend Tom that let's go to him because he cannot hit anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were exposed to this until night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At night, they let us back to the sleeping place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just illustrate you that we had a very strong camaraderie, around 10 o'clock they came to get us again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They read our name and somebody whose name I don't remember-- it was not a close friend, but a comrade-- said that you stay.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We go down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were six people went down instead of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as soon as he came down at first, they hit him, and he fell, and his mouth-- he had a seizure.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was froth coming out of his mouth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this frightened them so much that they stopped the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
